  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified vehicle control API for drones (ArduCopter) and rovers (ArduRover) via MAVSDK",
    "Scriptable missions with BasicRunner and StateMachine patterns",
    "Multi-vehicle coordination over ZMQ (leader/follower, swarms)",
    "Built-in safety checker with KML geofence and speed/altitude validation",
    "Non-blocking VehicleTask commands with progress tracking and cancellation",
    "QGroundControl .plan file support for preplanned trajectories",
    "AERPAW platform integration (OEO logging, checkpoints, safety pilot arming)",
    "v1 and v2 APIs with backward-compatible imports"
  ],
